OL,3,CMum called 'prostitute' on school run
OL,4,Camid Eastern European discrimination
OL,6,FAn Eastern European woman living in
OL,7,Fthe North East said she has been
OL,8,Fverbally abused while on the school
OL,9,Frun because of her nationality.
OL,11,FThe woman said a person shouted
OL,12,F"polish prostitute" at her while she
OL,13,Fwas walking her daughter to school.
OL,15,FHer testimony is part of a study which
OL,16,Flooks into the discrimination faced by
OL,17,FEastern European women across the
OL,18,FNorth East.
