OL,3,CMum called 'prostitute' on school run
OL,4,Camid Eastern European discrimination
OL,6,FOther women reported having been
OL,7,Fattacked in their own homes, verbally
OL,8,Fabused in local parks and even bullied
OL,9,Fin the workplace.
OL,11,FMolly Sharples has been speaking to
OL,12,Fthe women about their experiences of
OL,13,Fhate crime.
OL,15,FSunderland University surveyed 127
OL,16,Fwomen from different Eastern European
OL,17,Fcountries, living across the North
OL,18,FEast about their experiences with
OL,19,Fdiscrimination, based on both their
OL,20,Fnationality and their gender.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/13
