OL,3,CMum called 'prostitute' on school run
OL,4,Camid Eastern European discrimination
OL,6,FIt found that:
OL,8,F- 46% have experienced verbal abuse
OL,10,F- 36% had experienced racially
OL,11,Fmotivated and sex-based discrimination
OL,12,Fin their employment (25% by a
OL,13,Fbusiness, organisation or service
OL,14,Fprovider and 14% by healthcare
OL,15,Fproviders)
OL,17,F- 32% have experienced intimidation,
OL,18,Fthreats and harassment
OL,20,F- 18% had experienced property damage
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/13
