OL,6,F- 12% had been the victim of a
OL,7,Fphysical assault
OL,9,FOne of the women who took part in the
OL,10,Fstudy was "Anna". This is not her real
OL,11,Fname. She feared that if she was
OL,12,Fidentified, she would experience more
OL,13,Fabuse.
OL,15,FShe said she has faced hate crimes on
OL,16,F"many occasions", including being
OL,17,Ftargeted in her own home.
OL,19,FShe added: "A group of young people
OL,20,Fwere hanging around next to my house.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/13
