OL,3,CMum called 'prostitute' on school run
OL,4,Camid Eastern European discrimination
OL,6,F"I felt trapped and helpless because I
OL,7,Fdidn't know what to do. I called the
OL,8,Fpolice.
OL,10,F"I didn't feel safe. For three nights
OL,11,Fmy husband and I didn't sleep at all."
OL,13,F"I was afraid that those kids would
OL,14,Fcome back. I was paranoid about it for
OL,15,Fabout two weeks.
OL,17,F"I put up CCTV cameras.
OL,19,F"It was such a traumatic experience
OL,20,Fand I can't erase it from my memory."
