OL,6,FAnna said that these instances of
OL,7,Fdiscrimination happen in all aspects
OL,8,Fof her life including her workplace.
OL,10,FShe added: "People have shouted racial
OL,11,Fslurs at me at the park before in
OL,12,Ffront of my children.
OL,14,F"I get more of this abuse when I am
OL,15,Falone with the children, probably
OL,16,Fbecause I am a woman, I am more
OL,17,Fvulnerable, I can not react, but when
OL,18,Fthere is a man next to me, this
OL,19,Fdoesn't happen.
OL,26,@rD@LOUvD@AOU
