OL,6,F"If somebody is standing close, you
OL,7,Fknow two or three metres away, I try
OL,8,Fnot to speak my language because I
OL,9,Fdon't know if they will hear it and
OL,10,Fbecome abusive."
OL,12,FLeading the study was Dr Louise Harvey-
OL,13,FGolding. She said some of the
OL,14,Ftestimonies she received from the
OL,15,Fwomen were shocking and emotional.
OL,17,FShe said some of the women told her
OL,18,Fthey would avoid speaking in public
OL,19,Fplaces, even when in a group, to try
OL,20,Fand pass as British.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
