OL,4,Camid Eastern European discrimination
OL,6,FSome of the women also reported being
OL,7,Ftold not to speak their own language
OL,8,Fat work and being teased for their
OL,9,Fname and English speaking skills.
OL,11,FDr Harvey-Golding added: "Even the
OL,12,Fsexism and the sexual harassment has a
OL,13,Fracial element and that is what's
OL,14,Freally different about what Eastern
OL,15,FEuropean women are experiencing.
OL,17,F"Yes, all Eastern European people are
OL,18,Fexperiencing increased levels of
OL,19,Fracism in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/13
