OL,3,CMum called 'prostitute' on school run
OL,4,Camid Eastern European discrimination
OL,6,F"However Eastern European women are
OL,7,Fexperiencing something that is
OL,8,Fdistinct to that population.
OL,10,F"It's racism, it's sexual harassment,
OL,11,Fit's sexism and it's also classism and
OL,12,Fall of that comes together in a really
OL,13,Ftoxic mix that is having a huge impact
OL,14,Fon Eastern European women's lives."
OL,16,FJulia Wysocka is a community support
OL,17,Fofficer for International Community
OL,18,FOrganisation of Sunderland (ICOS).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/13
