OL,6,FShe runs a community support group for
OL,7,FEastern European women living in the
OL,8,FNorth East.
OL,10,FShe said they had been inundated with
OL,11,Fstories of hate crimes and
OL,12,Fdiscrimination from the women and so
OL,13,Fthey approached Sunderland University
OL,14,Fto look into it further.
OL,16,FMs Wysocka said was not shocked by the
OL,17,Fresults of the study.
