OL,6,FShe added: "There have always been
OL,7,Fissues with hate crime and anti-social
OL,8,Fbehaviour and ICOS has always
OL,9,Fsupported people with that but we have
OL,10,Fbeen seeing more women coming forward
OL,11,Fwith experiences with hate crime.
OL,13,F"Women who have been attacked on the
OL,14,Fstreet, been attacked in their place
OL,15,Fof work, even being attacked by their
OL,16,Fneighbours, which was obviously very
OL,17,Falarming.
OL,19,F"Women with lived experience wanted to
OL,20,Fbe involved and wanted their voices to
OL,21,Fbe heard.
