OL,6,F"The results haven't really shocked
OL,7,Fme. We knew the issues were there.
OL,9,F"It did give me more of a picture of
OL,10,Fwhat was happening. I have also been a
OL,11,Fvictim of hate crime so I know exactly
OL,12,Fwhat the women have been through."
